index_terms: DEPARTMENT OF HOUSING AND URBAN DEVELOPMENT
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Housing and Human Services authorizing application to and agreements with the U.S. Department of Housing and Urban Development, the Washington State Employment Security Department and United Way of King County for financial assistance for the operation of employment and training programs for low-income youth, increasing expenditure allowances in the 1992 Budgets of the Department of Housing and Human Services and Libraries, creating a position in the Department of Housing and Human Services, and making the necessary appropriations therefor.
